5
00:00:14,920 --> 00:00:18,836
This person was all crazy about using the
recording studio, but he never showed up.

6
00:00:18,860 --> 00:00:22,286
He doesn't even answer his
phone! I have to find him for sure.

7
00:00:22,310 --> 00:00:25,656
