8
00:00:25,680 --> 00:00:26,352
<i>Relief Supplies: Blanket, toothbrush,
toothpaste, soap, towel, toilet paper. Medicine</i>

9
00:00:26,376 --> 00:00:27,023
<i>Kit: Scissors, dressing, bandage, cold
medicine, painkillers, diarrhea medicine</i>

10
00:00:27,047 --> 00:00:27,557
<i>Food: Instant noodles, water,
seaweed, instant rice, rice, fruit</i>

11
00:00:27,581 --> 00:00:29,736
So, when are you coming back, Grandma?

12
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:33,006
Do you like it there that much?
You like it better than me?

13
00:00:33,030 --> 00:00:35,090
How could you be like that?

14
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:45,836
<i>She's old now but still
travels around all the time.</i>

15
00:00:45,860 --> 00:00:49,376
<i>You try and say something!
She listens to you.</i>

16
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:50,896
<i>I'm so worried.</i>

17
00:00:50,920 --> 00:00:54,766
Okay. I'll try and talk to her.

18
00:00:54,790 --> 00:00:55,836
Don't worry.

19
00:00:55,860 --> 00:00:57,903
Why do you have no energy?

20
00:00:57,928 --> 00:01:01,484
I'll send you an email
of what grandma needs.

21
