tell anyone about the recordings.

230
00:16:01,170 --> 00:16:02,990
So you've seen it.

231
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:08,016
Excuse me, that.

232
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:09,596
You don't have to use this.

233
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:13,970
But I want to. It looks cool.

234
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:24,106
Hello. Hello.

235
00:16:24,130 --> 00:16:27,580
When I give you the
signal you can start reading.

236
00:16:44,660 --> 00:16:47,556
ABCDEFG, HIJKLMN...

237
00:16:47,580 --> 00:16:52,416
- OPQRS....
- Let's try and read a bit more slower.

238
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:58,086
A, B, C, D...

239
00:16:58,110 --> 00:17:01,450
Sorry. Let's go a little
bit faster than that.

240
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:05,616
A, B, C...

241
