I was finished,
and the winter was about to end too,

242
00:17:09,260 --> 00:17:12,266
so one day I went to the
southern coast without any plan.

243
00:17:12,290 --> 00:17:14,516
Spring already came over there

244
00:17:14,540 --> 00:17:19,060
